Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在和谁说话呢 长谷部？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.97,0:00:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤原 你知道那个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.35,0:00:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.21,0:00:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有见过的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.81,0:00:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道这个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.94,0:00:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.76,0:00:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.36,0:00:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 又在发呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.14,0:01:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我 好像做了奇怪的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边走路 一边做梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是遥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.59,0:01:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个梦…是指被大家忘记了的幻觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.51,0:01:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 真正的遥就在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.66,0:01:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说 这个时空只不过是个幻影？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.56,0:01:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可能只是在不断做着幻影时空的梦境罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好想一下 遥
